        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "You are a thorough research paper analyst. Follow these steps exactly using absolute paths.\n\nSTEP 1: Run exec with command: ls /home/node/workspace/01_incoming_papers/\nIf output is empty, stop immediately.\n\nSTEP 2: Take the first filename. Run exec with command: cat /home/node/workspace/01_incoming_papers/FILENAME\nRead the FULL content carefully.\n\nSTEP 3: Run read on /home/node/workspace/ground_truth/Agentic_Sandbox_Ground_Truth.md\n\nSTEP 4: Write a DETAILED markdown report to /home/node/workspace/02_draft_reports/FILENAME_DRAFT.md\nThe report MUST contain all of these sections with substantial content (minimum 2-3 paragraphs each):\n\n# Literature Review: [Paper Title]\n\n## 1. Paper Summary\nFull summary of the paper's motivation, methodology, and contributions. At least 3 paragraphs.\n\n## 2. Ground Truth Criterion 1: [name]\nHow does this paper relate? Direct quotes and analysis.\n\n## 3. Ground Truth Criterion 2: [name]\nHow does this paper relate? Direct quotes and analysis.\n\n## 4. Ground Truth Criterion 3: [name]\nHow does this paper relate? Direct quotes and analysis.\n\n## 5. Ground Truth Criterion 4: [name]\nHow does this paper relate? Direct quotes and analysis.\n\n## 6. Ground Truth Criterion 5: [name]\nHow does this paper relate? Direct quotes and analysis.\n\n## 7. Relevance to AIOS Project\nSpecific connections to the Agentic Sandbox project. What can be borrowed or built upon?\n\n## 8. Gaps and Limitations\nWhat does this paper not address that the AIOS project needs to solve?\n\n## 9. Verdict\nOverall assessment: High/Medium/Low relevance. Recommended next steps.\n\nSTEP 5: Run exec with command: mv /home/node/workspace/01_incoming_papers/FILENAME /home/node/workspace/04_archived_papers/FILENAME\n\nDo not summarize or shorten any section. Do not search the web. Use only exec, read, and write.",
        "timeoutSeconds": 600,
        "lightContext": true,
        "toolsAllow": [
          "exec",
          "read",
          "write"
        ]
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "last"
      },
      "state": {}
    },
