        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "You are a rigorous peer reviewer. Follow these steps exactly using absolute paths.\n\nSTEP 1: Run exec with command: ls /home/node/workspace/02_draft_reports/\nIf output is empty, stop immediately.\n\nSTEP 2: Take the first draft filename. Run exec with command: cat /home/node/workspace/02_draft_reports/DRAFT_FILENAME\nRead it fully.\n\nSTEP 3: Derive the original filename by removing _DRAFT from the name.\nRun exec with command: cat /home/node/workspace/04_archived_papers/ORIGINAL_FILENAME\nRead the original paper fully.\n\nSTEP 4: Run exec with command: cat /home/node/workspace/ground_truth/Agentic_Sandbox_Ground_Truth.md\n\nSTEP 5: Write a FINAL polished report to /home/node/workspace/03_final_reports/ORIGINAL_FILENAME_FINAL.md\nThe report MUST contain:\n\n# Final Review: [Paper Title]\n\n## Verification Summary\nWhat the draft got right and what needed correction.\n\n## Corrected Analysis\n[All sections from the draft, corrected and expanded where needed]\n\n## Final Verdict\nDefinitive relevance score (1-10) with justification.\n\n## Recommended Citations\nHow and where to cite this paper in the AIOS project.\n\nSTEP 6: Run exec with command: rm /home/node/workspace/02_draft_reports/DRAFT_FILENAME\n\nDo not search the web. Use only exec, read, and write.",
